76
00:11:53,212 --> 00:11:55,792
Sure, there's a phone just behind you.

77
00:11:56,042 --> 00:11:57,882
Thank you.

78
00:12:03,433 --> 00:12:05,473
Gloria? Hi, it's me.

79
00:12:06,014 --> 00:12:09,524
Good, good. How's Charlie?

80
00:12:09,774 --> 00:12:12,564
Hi, honey. How was your day at school?

81
00:12:12,814 --> 00:12:15,944
Yeah? What was the best part?

82
00:12:16,195 --> 00:12:19,905
